        title: `Use Call Screen for unknown numbers (Pixel phones)`,
        content: `On Google Pixel phones, when an unknown call comes in, you will see a "Screen call" button alongside the answer and reject buttons. Tap "Screen call" and Google Assistant will answer and ask the caller to identify themselves. Watch the live transcription on screen. If it is clearly spam, tap "Hang up." If it sounds legitimate, tap "Answer" to join the call.`,
